Package it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.longs

Class Long2BooleanMaps

java.lang.Object
it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.longs.Long2BooleanMaps
public final class Long2BooleanMaps extends Object
A class providing static methods and objects that do useful things with type-specific maps.

    • singleton

      public static Long2BooleanMap singleton(long key, boolean value)
      Returns a type-specific immutable map containing only the specified pair. The returned map is serializable and cloneable.

      Note that albeit the returned map is immutable, its default return value may be changed.

      Parameters:
      key - the only key of the returned map.
      value - the only value of the returned map.
      Returns:
      a type-specific immutable map containing just the pair &lt;key,value&gt;.
